features: Travel Must Haves: BAGSMART 7 set packing cubes include 1 Large size (13.8’’×3.9’’×13.8’’) for jackets, sweaters, trousers. 3 Medium size (6.9’’×3.5’’×13.8’’) for shirts, T-shirts, shorts. 2 Small size (6.9’’×3.5’’×6.9'') for underwear, socks. 1 Shoe bag (19.7’’×14.5’’). Various sizes are suitable for storing different items to meet your various storage needs.

Keep Shape Well: Unique mini plastic frame wraps around to keep its shape upright even when empty. It allows you to easily pack your clothes into packing organizers without having to hold the bag with one hand, saving you valuable time and making packing a lot easier.

Tear Resistant To Last: The suitcase organizers bag set is made of high-quality nylon and high-density mesh, which is not easy to wear or tear under frequent use. Sturdy double zipper design, smooth to use, allows you to open and close the packing cube set with ease.

Lightweight Travel Essentials: Light fabric ensures your clothes will fit neatly in your luggage without adding extra weight. These travel cubes are perfect when you want to save weight and save space in your carry-on, suitcase or backpack.

Versatile and Multipurpose: Whether you're carrying airline carry-on luggage, duffel bags, backpacks or handbags, these luggage packing bags fit compactly to maximize space. You can take these travel accessories on business trips, camping adventures, and vacations to keep your clothes organized and easy to find, or use them at home as cabinet storage organizers to keep your wardrobe tidy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love my packing cubes!
reviews.reviewText: I never travel without them now! It helps to keep clothes organized in the suitcase instead of everything thrown in together. Now instead of taking half my clothes out of the suitcase in order to put together an outfit and then having to refold everything to fit it back in to the suitcase, I just take out a couple of cubes, take out what I need from them and put them back in the suitcase. They are perfectly sized to fit in my suitcase too! I didn't think I would use the handles but I do. It's a nice touch. I like that they have netting on top so not only can I see in to see what's inside but I feel like it helps to keep my clothes aired out while stuck in a suitcase for a week or two. I've used them for several trips, including two international trips, and they have held up very well. I feel they are well-made and will hold up for many more trips. I just wish I could order the different sizes individually. I would love a couple more of just the small size.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Buy these before your trip!
reviews.reviewText: After multiple trips where I said I would buy packing cubes next time, I finally bought them and boy, do I regret not getting them sooner. My partner has had this same set for years and his are well loved and still working perfectly.As advertised, they really help you keep your bag organized. Plenty of bags with compartments and varying sizes means you can sort your items. It comes with what I'm told is a shoe bag, but personally I use it for the really dirty laundry.The zippers feel sturdy and well made, and each cube is structured so that they retain their shape. The carrying handles are nice as well, makes it easy to pull the cubes out of your suitcase and put them somewhere like the dresser or in the closet.Fully packed cubes fill up 50-75%% of my standard 24" Samsonite Winfield suitcase, which is perfect because the rest can be my shoes/toiletries.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars More structure than excoected
reviews.reviewText: I’ve used packing cubes for years as they help keep my luggage organized while traveling. These were a bit less flexible than expected. Nice product but had strong structured wires for durability that made them less flexible and more rigid. Mesh was a bit rough for finer clothes. Noticed seams were not aligned and I was concerned about durability after reading some reviewed. Nice product but not sure how effective the space saving feature would be with the rigidity if the frame. I returned
